Joe Conley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Conley 0 Joe Conley (March 3, 1928 – July 7, 2013) was an American actor who played many small roles on television and is most remembered for his role as the storekeeper Ike Godsey in The Waltons.
